{"tid":1115176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Leica 新廣告重現 1989 年天安門場景","createTime":"2019-04-19T04:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T15:13:42.000Z","uid":32311,"like":110,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"10c8150921a73ad1a1816d24f7e298e0b555781e","tid":1115176,"uid":32311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eNX2GmF6Zbw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeNX2GmF6Zbw&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQ4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=4f8fbd4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eNX2GmF6Zbw</a><br />\n<br />\n睇下華為今次點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c17496c417d73d6667c34c09ca0bf8e54f088c6","tid":1115176,"uid":32311,"like":59,"dislike":0,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:08:32.000Z","msg":"不得了，德國相機、鏡頭歷史名廠 Leica 做咗一件係中國大陸應該係「關公災難」級的舉動！ 最新廣告「The Hunt」竟然重現北京 1989 年天安門的場景，著名的「坦克人」都出現！ 立刻睇睇原片！<br />\n<br />\n華為停止合作？ Leica 新廣告重現 1989 年天安門場景<br />\n<br />\n其實，Leica 的廣告一向水準都非常高，過往都多次獲得獎項殊榮。今次「The Hunt」呢個廣告係 Saatchi &amp; Saatchi 盛世廣告巴西分公司推出。呢間廣告公司其實好厲害，專門做高格調品牌，香港分公司客戶包括最大的銀行、最大的汽車品牌、甚至香港政府部門！ 廣告公司 Youtube 原片已顯示已刪除，所以只能比第三方 LINK 各位睇，請點擊這裡觀看（如失效請報告，會有後備片）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n長達 5 分鐘的廣告到底想講咩呢？ 根據 Adsoftheworld 介紹（內文原片已被刪除），明確地指出「The Hunt」透過重現 1989 年天安門廣場的民眾抗議行動，也穿插著其他世界各地的黑暗面，從戰爭到殘酷的野外，用片中的多個角色嘗試表達出當時這些角色在真實環境所展示的勇氣。有份參與導演工作的 Kid Burro 更指出，本片難得地擁有這麼大的創作空間。用了超過一年的時間，去研究不同攝影師的歷史故事，包括當中他們曾經遇到的困難，如何克服並成就各種歷史經典照片。<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/dc/talk/1430/25813/1/?fbclid=IwAR3tduOjsQUFuAA37Inf_H7EDkoMGV6bmnVDPZ7P9xXOcOP5chcep2EZd48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fdc%2Ftalk%2F1430%2F25813%2F1%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3tduOjsQUFuAA37Inf_H7EDkoMGV6bmnVDPZ7P9xXOcOP5chcep2EZd48&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQ4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=55c14a23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/dc/talk/1430/25813/1/?fbclid=IwAR3tduOjsQUFuAA37Inf_H7EDkoMGV6bmnVDPZ7P9xXOcOP5chcep2EZd48</a><br />\n<br />\n[/url]"},{"pid":"f3bded5ab75f84f8e29c6bd536b59a767a048522","tid":1115176,"uid":150807,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"Leica<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa56f746edc5a97585c664ac916b533e6403edb9","tid":1115176,"uid":155137,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"華為手機用leica<br />\n咁應該買定唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394d8c5f68e2444bd103cf8fa7eea4efe7c028da","tid":1115176,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fa56f746edc5a97585c664ac916b533e6403edb9","tid":1115176,"uid":155137,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"華為手機用leica<br />\n咁應該買定唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:42:17.000Z","msg":"係leica認證者"},{"pid":"96dc44d1f38a579647714d8b833de53225614175","tid":1115176,"uid":231725,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"好撚正<br />\n個廣告"},{"pid":"dfce3b99734617d972215d5b18ea9c9ae8ca96c2","tid":1115176,"uid":56147,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:14:49.000Z","msg":"Leica ...好想支持下  可惜對我黎講太貴"},{"pid":"a8c8a8fc4a352ed5a465f969587d2c4c6198ebfd","tid":1115176,"uid":46155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":